    "chinese_traditional": "Demon. Rules over the magma-flowing, burning plains in the corner of the demon realm. Extremely powerful, she gained the title of \"Queen of the Inferno\" from her ability to manipulate the fires of hell at will.\n\nShe has lived for centuries and is acquainted with the head of Nomad, Edwin Black. But they went separate ways because of conflicting views. She also rarely leaves the demon realm to venture into other worlds.",
    "spanish": "Demon. Rules over the magma-flowing, burning plains in the corner of the demon realm. Extremely powerful, she gained the title of \"Queen of the Inferno\" from her ability to manipulate the fires of hell at will.\n\nShe has lived for centuries and is acquainted with the head of Nomad, Edwin Black. But they went separate ways because of conflicting views. She also rarely leaves the demon realm to venture into other worlds."
